&lt;li&gt;Assist in the analysis and design of bridges, culverts, retaining walls, and related structural components.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support preparation of plans, specifications, and engineering calculations in accordance with AASHTO and state DOT standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize engineering software (e.g., MicroStation, OpenRoads, or structural analysis tools) to support design and drafting tasks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Aid in the development of 3D models and structural layouts for transportation infrastructure projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with quantity take-offs, cost estimating, and construction documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with multidisciplinary teams on transportation projects including roadway, geotechnical, and hydrological analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide general project support across multiple assignments as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
