&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Civil Engineering (Structural emphasis preferred) from an ABET/EAC-accredited program.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engineer-in-Training (EIT) or Fundamentals of Engineering (FE) certification required or ability to obtain within 6 months.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1-3 years of experience in transportation structures or structural design preferred.&lt;/li&gt;

